sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as ML Model/Client
    participant OnlineService as Online Store Service<br/>80/443 TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant OnlinePod as Online Store Pod<br/>6566/6567 TCP
    participant RegistryService as Registry Service<br/>80/443 TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Storage as Storage Backend<br/>Redis/Cassandra/DB
    participant Notebook as Data Scientist Notebook
    participant OfflineService as Offline Store Service<br/>80/443 TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant OfflinePod as Offline Store Pod<br/>8815/8816 TCP
    participant ObjectStore as S3/GCS/Snowflake<br/>443 TCP HTTPS
    participant CronJob as Materialization CronJob
    participant FeastCLI as Feast CLI/Client
    participant RegistryPod as Registry Pod<br/>6570-6573 TCP

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval for Inference

    Client->>OnlineService: POST /get-online-features<br/>Auth: OIDC/K8s RBAC<br/>TLS 1.2+ (if HTTPS)
    OnlineService->>OnlinePod: Forward request<br/>Port 6566/6567
    OnlinePod->>RegistryService: Get feature metadata<br/>TLS 1.2+ (if HTTPS)
    RegistryService-->>OnlinePod: Feature schema
    OnlinePod->>Storage: Fetch feature values<br/>Native Protocol, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: DB Credentials
    Storage-->>OnlinePod: Feature data
    OnlinePod-->>OnlineService: Feature vector
    OnlineService-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Notebook,ObjectStore: Flow 2: Historical Feature Retrieval for Training

    Notebook->>OfflineService: POST /get-historical-features<br/>Auth: OIDC/K8s RBAC<br/>TLS 1.2+ (if HTTPS)
    OfflineService->>OfflinePod: Forward request<br/>Port 8815/8816
    OfflinePod->>RegistryService: Get feature metadata<br/>TLS 1.2+ (if HTTPS)
    RegistryService-->>OfflinePod: Feature schema
    OfflinePod->>ObjectStore: Fetch historical data<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Cloud IAM/Credentials
    ObjectStore-->>OfflinePod: Historical features
    OfflinePod-->>OfflineService: Feature dataset
    OfflineService-->>Notebook: Parquet/DataFrame Response

    Note over CronJob,Storage: Flow 3: Feature Materialization (Offline to Online)

    CronJob->>RegistryService: Get materialization config<br/>TLS 1.2+ (if HTTPS)
    RegistryService-->>CronJob: Feature definitions
    CronJob->>OfflineService: Read historical features<br/>TLS 1.2+ (if HTTPS)
    OfflineService-->>CronJob: Feature batch
    CronJob->>OnlineService: POST /push<br/>TLS 1.2+ (if HTTPS)
    OnlineService->>OnlinePod: Write features
    OnlinePod->>Storage: Persist features<br/>Native Protocol, TLS 1.2+
    Storage-->>OnlinePod: ACK
    OnlinePod-->>OnlineService: Success
    OnlineService-->>CronJob: Materialization complete

    Note over FeastCLI,ObjectStore: Flow 4: Registry Management

    FeastCLI->>RegistryService: gRPC/HTTP /proto/* or /registry/*<br/>Port 80/443<br/>Auth: OIDC/K8s RBAC<br/>TLS 1.2+ (if HTTPS)
    RegistryService->>RegistryPod: Forward request<br/>Port 6570-6573
    RegistryPod->>ObjectStore: Read/write registry data<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Credentials/IAM
    ObjectStore-->>RegistryPod: Registry state
    RegistryPod-->>RegistryService: Response
    RegistryService-->>FeastCLI: Feature definitions
